<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-65-0438 </DOCNO><TEXT>Effect of single-mode helical disturbance of tokamak magnetic field onthe motion of high-energy ions produced in thermonuclear reactions isinvestigated. The value of the disturbance critical amplitude, sufficientfor drift surface destruction and appearance of energetic particle stochasticdiffusion, is evaluated. Analytic evaluations are compared with numericalsimulation results.</TEXT></DOC>